column5: Well folks, here is my turn to say please vote for me.  Thanks for looking and to those that vote too!!!  http://www.wfn.tv/gearweek/view.php?entry=129
LOL!! I would - but I'm in that contest too!
Alright, tks.  Done, you got a 5 from me too, that's a lot of gear!

Hahaha!! I know!! My fiancee thinks I'm crazy about it!! hahaha - I told her, EH! its just as bad when a woman has to have 50 different purses....just like you, we need different rods/reels for different fishing applications! LOL!!
Another guy from the OFC group joined the contest too... I think its "MEPPS"....Anyway, Good luck to you bud!
Ok, so who is des connelly from temagami?  LMAO!  You are one crazy person... HAHA  *edit*  yes I voted for you too as that's just wrong...

did you find it and call Des on it?  LoL!

Thank you to all that have voted and a pre-thanks to any new votes!

I'm there too if anyone wants to vote for me.  http://www.wfn.tv/gearweek/view.php?entry=7  I sent in submission for the "Live to fish" contest a while ago. I had over 100 votes from people at work, friends etc. but they kept putting me back to zero.  Cheers and good luck everyone.  Paul
